      "weather": "Overcast",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRY TO RELAX (3) jumped from the inside and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 1.3 lengths (22.03) behind Federal Blast at this track. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Top chance in this line up. COLONEL'S DREAM (1) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish third, beaten 2 lengths, (23.95) at Rockhampton. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Hard to beat again. TOMMY'S WHISKY (2) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 8th at this track following on from a third place finish (28.91) there the start prior. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Has ability and is one of the better chances. TEX GUNN (5) is always hard to beat when he races here at this trip.",
